RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.MARGIN_COMPONENT ,B.DESCRIPTION ,A.SEQ_NO ,A.BASIS_AMT_TAG ,A.DEFAULT_MARGIN_RATE ,A.MARGIN_BASIS FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_ICCF_MARGIN A, LFTMS_MARGIN_DEFINITION B WHERE A.PRODUCT_CODE = ? AND A.COMPONENT = ? AND A.MARGIN_COMPONENT = B.MARGIN_COMPONENT
SELECT A.COMPONENT, COMPONENT_DESCRIPTION FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_ICCF A WHERE PRODUCT = ? AND NVL(STOP_APPLICATION,'N') = 'N' AND RATE_TYPE = 'F'

SELECT A.BORROWER_DRAWDOWN_PRODUCT ,B.PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION FROM LBTMS_FACILITY_DD_PRODUCT A, OLTMS_PRODUCT B, OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD C ,OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR D WHERE A.BORROWER_TRANCHE_PRODUCT = ? AND A.PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(? ) AND A.BORROWER_DRAWDOWN_PRODUCT =B.PRODUCT_CODE AND B.PRODUCT_CODE = C.PRODUCT AND B.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND B.AUTH_STAT='A' AND D.PRODUCT_CODE = B.PRODUCT_CODE AND D.BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND D.USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID AND C.PROD_SCH_TYPE= DECODE(?,'N','N',C.PROD_SCH_TYPE)

SELECT DISTINCT COUNTERPARTY, CUSTOMER_NAME1, SSI_MNEMONIC, SETTLEMENT_SEQ_NO FROM OLTM_INSTR A,OLTMS_CUSTOMER B WHERE COUNTERPARTY = ? AND A.AUTH_STAT ='A' AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND BRANCH IN (?,'ALL') AND MODULE IN (?,'AL') AND PRODUCT_CODE IN (?,'ALL') AND B.CUSTOMER_NO=A.COUNTERPARTY and B.RECORD_STAT = 'O'
